replies.body:
You know what? While I still do not agree very much with what my limited understanding leads me to believe was your premise in your original post, I would like to apologize for making so many antagonistic posts in your thread.

It is difficult for me to come to an understanding without the aid of body language and vocal tone, but I am sorry that I (correctly or incorrectly) assumed ill intent of you.

{{sticker:sg-soraka}}
